<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Prayer for the New Year</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Jan 02, 2016 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
A simple prayer for the new year:
</p>

 <p>
God of grace and wisdom <br></br>
create in me a new desire, <br></br>
that I may be no more, and no less, <br></br>
than who you created me to be. <br></br></p>

 <p>
For that, dear Lord, is surely enough. <br></br></p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


